		<span class="story-byline">
	
				
			Posted
				by 
		
		
			
				  <a href="https://twitter.com/BeauHD" rel="nofollow">BeauHD</a>
			
		
		

		
		
		<time id="fhtime-173694578" datetime="on Tuesday April 30, 2024 @11:30PM">on Tuesday April 30, 2024 @11:30PM</time>
		
		
			 from the <span class="dept-text">news-that-blows</span> dept.
		
